# Three deliberate bugs — `aix check` finds each one with its exact location.
E post title:str!<=200, author>user, rank:int=high, created@
R post list:mine, get, create, update:[titel], delete
# bugs: (1) author>user — no `user` entity. (2) rank:int=high — int default isn't an integer.
# (3) update:[titel] — typo, not a field (verifier suggests "title").
